pull.title: Log timestamp
pull.body:
Add timestamps to debug.log when -logtimestamps is set.
Follow up to: 
https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/91

repo.name: bitcoin
repo.description: Bitcoin (dont fork from here, fork from bitcoin/bitcoin)

events.message: Add timestamp prefix to each line in the debug log (this time with human-readable times)
Only log timestamps if -logtimestamps is set.

events.body: jhyslop mentioned that he is doing a full rewrite of logging (separating debug of various parts, etc).  I'd assume wait for him to finish his code before doing anything here.
Opened an issue related to this patch: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/119
